<title>HUNG TUAH U CH275</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Amah thawng nungmi nih Amah kha kan thlau, Hmuh than nak caan kha a
 tlung, Kan Pa kan kawl zungzal mi kha kan hngal lo, A duh lo rian kha kan
 tuan.

[C1]
   Hungtuah u (Hung tuah u, tuah u) Hung tuah u, (Hung tuah u, tuah u)
   Amah min thangthatnak (Amah min thangthatnak) hmun ah (thangthatnak hmun
   ah, Chak le thlang mi vial hung tuah u, Vancung khua tha kan phak lai.

[V2]
 Tuu tlaumi bangin kan Bawi sinin kan tlau, Sualnak hlingbur a kan
 donh, Kir than awkah a kan auhnak thawng ngai tuah, A thangthatnak hla sa
 u.

[C2]
   Hungtuah u (Hung tuah u, tuah u) Hung tuah u, (Hung tuah u, tuah u)
   Amah min thangthatnak (Amah min thangthatnak) hmun ah (thangthatnak hmun
   ah, Chak le thlang mi vial hung tuah u, Vancung khua tha kan phak lai.

[V3]
 Kan pipu thawk in kan duh cio bikmi kha, Kannih sin a rung phan cang,
 Cu si ca thangthat u, a kan Khamhtu Bawi, Thluachuah ruahpi rung sur seh.

[C3]
   Hungtuah u (Hung tuah u, tuah u) Hung tuah u, (Hung tuah u, tuah u)
   Amah min thangthatnak (Amah min thangthatnak) hmun ah (thangthatnak hmun
   ah, Chak le thlang mi vial hung tuah u, Vancung khua tha kan phak lai.

[V4]
 Kannih kan sunparnak ni kha a nai cang, Khua zong a dei dengmang cang,
 Bawipa nih ral vialte a tei dih cang i, Vawlei cung a pen zungzal.

[C4]
   Hungtuah u (Hung tuah u, tuah u) Hung tuah u, (Hung tuah u, tuah u)
   Amah min thangthatnak (Amah min thangthatnak) hmun ah (thangthatnak hmun
   ah, Chak le thlang mi vial hung tuah u, Vancung khua tha kan phak lai.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
</song>